    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously gotta see this beauty\u2014it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve pampered this car since day one, keeping it tucked away in the garage and making sure the interior stays absolutely spotless. It drives like a total dream, and honestly, you'd be hard-pressed to find another one in such incredible shape. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved and cared for, this is definitely it. Feel free to reach out if you want to take a look!",
