    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a museum-grade FD3S RX-7 featuring a numbers-matching 13B-REW rotary engine. This example demonstrates flawless sequential turbocharger transition and maintains factory-spec compression across all rotor faces. The chassis retains its original torsional rigidity, supported by unblemished double-wishbone suspension components and a precise Torsen limited-slip differential. Meticulously maintained with a focus on thermal management and vacuum system integrity, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of 50/50 weight distribution engineering. Zero oxidation on the undercarriage and a pristine interior with no UV-induced plastics degradation.",
